{"tid":2301374,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"決定走上價投呢條不歸路⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-11-26T09:06:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:33:53.000Z","uid":40121,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"db620d6609beedfabcb535da3dc561a56deed242","tid":2301374,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:06:15.000Z","msg":"大家好吖又係我<span class=\"gold\">三支金流</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時都係先執好哂出文再放上連登<br />\n比左個錯覺大家我係會專業嚴謹分析<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（有巴打仲問我係咪分析師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n實際上我同大家一樣都係<span class=\"red\">初學業餘</span>的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左比大家感受一下<span class=\"orange\">研究思考投資其實都係會周圍盲中中</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我今次決定一反傳統 係連登出個<span class=\"orange\">講故式連載po記錄我研究嘅過程</span> 最後先至整理成文<br />\n中間<span class=\"red\">撞左啲咩板 諗錯啲咩</span> 大家可以見到同即時feedback到比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n過程我預可能一個星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家想追睇嘅歡迎用追故模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推推我個blog<span class=\"gold\">三支金流的資本掙扎</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://3gcashflow.blogspot.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2F3gcashflow.blogspot.com&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=b78036ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://3gcashflow.blogspot.com</a><br />\n<br />\n今次呢個研究我採用左<span class=\"red\">google大法</span>做起點<br />\n最後發現左兩個新嘅asset class：<span class=\"orange\">BDC</span> 同 <span class=\"gold\">Royalty Trust</span><br />\n有咩好有咩唔好 請容我娓娓道來⋯⋯"},{"pid":"0a793281b9d93c01c3b0a7d91ab87179a28f0e86","tid":2301374,"uid":209773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"會窮"},{"pid":"9c11727e4fde72d52a8db4ac45152ea4eb9ea924","tid":2301374,"uid":249207,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:07:02.000Z","msg":"（與數簿巴搞基之路）"},{"pid":"15dc4b11117ad7ea1f5a4d58eae834fec450470d","tid":2301374,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a793281b9d93c01c3b0a7d91ab87179a28f0e86","tid":2301374,"uid":209773,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:06:40.000Z","msg":"會窮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:07:22.000Z","msg":"巴打接到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波"},{"pid":"b7353777861f94b44ca2368c4b356de43a31e2a1","tid":2301374,"uid":97772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d423bff6dcb78b2d4695b788414d79c5a60e84e9","tid":2301374,"uid":215634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"有無facebook page?<br />\n<br />\n價投從來唔係不歸路。所有投資必定回歸至future cash flow，對cash flow判斷錯誤，或以過高價買入資產，長遠必有損失。"},{"pid":"6753c1a4b2d2d2abf75a1eac1107e28272b2b2be","tid":2301374,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:15:34.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"1cbfeb589cff1d953cc0930175f14cbf93ca7726","tid":2301374,"uid":40121,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:15:56.000Z","msg":"所謂Google大法係最近朋友介紹的<br />\n事緣佢推左隻IMB比我 話係收息股我應該會中意叫我望下<br />\n我就好感歎點解佢可以搵到咁多得意野 我成日都搵唔撚到<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\">佢：Google⋯⋯<br />\n我：但你搵咩Keyword啊？<br />\n佢：英國 收息股 之後睇下人地推乜</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我頓時覺得自己係一個大on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nanyway自從學識左（？）Google大法之後我久唔久就搵啲Keyword睇下人地推乜<br />\n早兩日我就睇屎忽痕想要啲月派息股加強組合嘅現金流<br />\n就用<span class=\"gold\">「Monthly Dividend Stock」</span>做keyword搵到一篇咁嘅文：<a href=\"https://money.usnews.com/investing/dividends/slideshows/7-monthly-dividend-stocks-with-double-digit-yields\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmoney.usnews.com%2Finvesting%2Fdividends%2Fslideshows%2F7-monthly-dividend-stocks-with-double-digit-yields&d=ME9RTGLMBg%2Fi%2BHfTLk0cjBR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=6e5fe810\" target=\"_blank\">https://money.usnews.com/investing/dividends/slideshows/7-monthly-dividend-stocks-with-double-digit-yields</a><br />\n一入到去全撚部都高單位/隻位dividend yield<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嚇死寶寶<br />\n不過邊有咁爽吖 果然第一隻AGNC就係<span class=\"gold\">惡名邵著嘅mortgage REITs</span>"},{"pid":"a2a44b055dcd82a606d7d7d9b511f8b192d49e4d","tid":2301374,"uid":40121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d423bff6dcb78b2d4695b788414d79c5a60e84e9","tid":2301374,"uid":215634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:11:29.000Z","msg":"有無facebook page?<br />\n<br />\n價投從來唔係不歸路。所有投資必定回歸至future cash flow，對cash flow判斷錯誤，或以過高價買入資產，長遠必有損失。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:16:50.000Z","msg":"巴打認真左 我係標題黨來的<br />\n開page/ig你係咪gchi先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ae7ae16b0c0299a84d43129036e39537c662d6","tid":2301374,"uid":40121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:28:41.000Z","msg":"mREITs 嘅惡名 應該都要追番去 2008年次按風暴<br />\n以前啲銀行批左筆mortgage之後就要揸住筆貸款成世<br />\n但自從有人發明左Mortgage Backed Securities MBS之後 銀行可以將批左出去嘅Mortgage包裝成MBS賣出去快速實現盈利<br />\n於是銀行同其他按揭機構就放寛哂啲批核標準 多啲尼密啲手咁批按揭<br />\n甚至會批出「subprime（次級）」按揭借埋首期比買家 甚至連無業游民都申請到按揭<br />\n最後因為貸款實在係質量太差 開始違約 買左MBS嘅機構發現手上嘅只係廢紙 長達十年嘅蕭條就咁就開始左<br />\nmREITs 就係通過持有MBS賺錢作分派嘅「REITs」<br />\n本質上就係借錢番尼再借出去套利差 <br />\n<br />\n佢本身唔涉及營運物業 真係營運棟野果啲叫eREITs equity REITs"},{"pid":"6a1fc84a78cc30b1c1190e4b347085d10a0ebec7","tid":2301374,"uid":40121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"AGNC 嘅MBS係Agency MBS<br />\n姐係有政府機構核準嘅MBS 理論上會安全啲<br />\n但下一隻就係non-Agency嘅mREITs ARR 我直接skip左<br />\n心有餘悸啊大佬<br />\n<br />\n接下來三隻 GLAD HRZN PSEC 三隻都係對中小企業放款機構<br />\n三隻都10%以上股息率<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正喎 咁咪姐係可以通過佢地投資中小企呢啲小巿場？<br />\n中小企債固然高息 但係財政未必好穩建<br />\n但如果係啲高順位債搭配一個分散嘅portfolio 其實應該風險可控<br />\n而且中小企呢啲反映國民經濟嘅東西 我對美國經濟有信心！<br />\n買買買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪住先 巿場唔係on9的 咁高yield肯定有啲問題<br />\n於是我又用google大法搵下呢啲叫咩公司"},{"pid":"e9a29536cd14ecd3551211d9f321d9f821c9402c","tid":2301374,"uid":249207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a1fc84a78cc30b1c1190e4b347085d10a0ebec7","tid":2301374,"uid":40121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:39:09.000Z","msg":"AGNC 嘅MBS係Agency MBS<br />\n姐係有政府機構核準嘅MBS 理論上會安全啲<br />\n但下一隻就係non-Agency嘅mREITs ARR 我直接skip左<br />\n心有餘悸啊大佬<br />\n<br />\n接下來三隻 GLAD HRZN PSEC 三隻都係對中小企業放款機構<br />\n三隻都10%以上股息率<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n正喎 咁咪姐係可以通過佢地投資中小企呢啲小巿場？<br />\n中小企債固然高息 但係財政未必好穩建<br />\n但如果係啲高順位債搭配一個分散嘅portfolio 其實應該風險可控<br />\n而且中小企呢啲反映國民經濟嘅東西 我對美國經濟有信心！<br />\n買買買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪住先 巿場唔係on9的 咁高yield肯定有啲問題<br />\n於是我又用google大法搵下呢啲叫咩公司"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T09:43:44.000Z","msg":"High Yield 唔代表一定有問題"},{"pid":"77d184b9ecfa4745daa7eba8b23caee14c1